ich starred Diane Keaton.}}</ref> it was not included in Disney Channel's 100 Original Movies celebration that aired in May\u2013June 2016,<ref name=\"BuzzFeed\">{{cite web |first=Casey|last=Rackham |url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/caseyrackham/omg-the-disney-channel-original-movie-schedule-is-here |title=The Complete Disney Channel Original Movie Schedule Is Here And It\u2019s Amazing |work=[[BuzzFeed]] |date=May 24, 2016 |access-date=2017-03-15}}</ref> and Disney Channel considers 1997's ''[[Under Wraps (film)|Under Wraps]]'' to be the first official Disney Channel Original Movie.<ref>{{cite web |first=Patrick|last=Hipes |url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/disney-channel-original-movie-the-swap-dcom-marathon-1201741163/ |title=Disney Channel Original Movie \u2018The Swap\u2019 Set As Network Plans 100-Pic Celebration |work=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |date=April 20, 2016 |access-date=2016-06-27 |quote=The news comes as Disney Channel today unveiled plans for the 100th DCOM Celebration, a summer programming marathon centered on the airing of the network\u2019s 100th original move since 1997 \u2014 the first movie was ''Under Wraps'', and the 100th will be a reimagining of the 1987 film ''Adventures In Babysitting'' which doesn\u2019t have an airdate yet. }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Marc|last=Snetiker |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/06/22/disney-channel-original-movie-stories |title=Disney Channel Original Movies: 12 little-known stories |work=[[Entertainment Weekly]] |date=June 22, 2016 |access-date=2016-06-26 |quote=Disney Channel considers 1997\u2019s ''Under Wraps'' as its first official DCOM...}}</ref>}}\n|}\n;Notes\n{{Reflist|group=\"Note\"}}\n\n==Disney Channel Original Movies==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Film\n! scope=\"col\" data-sort-type=\"date\" | Premiere date\n! scope=\"col\" data-sort-type=\"number\" | Ratings<br/>(millions)\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | {{Abbr|Ref(s)|References}}\