hes]]''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | 7.0\n|<ref name=\"Umstead071122\" />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2006\n|''[[The Cheetah Girls 2]]''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | 7.8\n|<ref name=\"TCG2#2\" /><ref name=\"TCG2#3\" /><ref name=\"TCG2#1\" />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2007\n|''[[High School Musical 2]]''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | 17.2\n|<ref name=\"Variety-HM2\" /><ref name=\"TNYT-HSM2\" /><ref name=\"eonline.com\">{{cite news|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/2216/camp-rocks-hsm-but-not-hsm2|title=Camp Rocks HSM, But Not HSM2|author=|date=June 21, 2008|work=E! Online}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1683&dat=20070819&id=ReYeAAAAIBAJ&sjid=s0UEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1758,6043860|title='High School Musical' sets cable TV records|author=Dave Itzkoff|date=August 19, 2007|work=Milwaukee Journal Sentinel|via=Google}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.tvweek.com/in-depth/2007/08/disneys-high-school-musical-2/ |title=Disney's \u2018High School Musical 2\u2032 is Most-Watched Cable Telecast Ever  |author= |date=August 18, 2007 |work=TVWeek}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/ratings/2007/08/20/disney-channels-high-school-musical-2-breaks-cable-telecast-records--25260/20070820disney01/ |title=Ratings \u2013 Disney Channel's \"High School Musical 2\" Breaks Cable Telecast Records |author=|date=August 20, 2007 |work=[[The Futon Critic]]}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2008\n|''[[Camp Rock]]''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | 8.9\n|<ref name=\"Variety-CR\" /><ref name=\"TVG-CR\" /><ref name=\"TNYT-CR\" /><ref name=\"eonline.com\"/><ref name=\"Us Magazine\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2009\n|''[[Wizards of Waverly Place: The Movie]]''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | 11.4\n|<ref name=\"WoWP:TM#1\" /><ref name=\"WoWP:TM#2\" />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2010\n|''[[Camp Rock 2: The Final Jam]