y digestible, often cheesy, sometimes awful, and always a delightful way to escape reality for a little bit.}}</ref><ref name=mtv0>{{cite web |last=Grant|first=Stacey |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2893515/disney-channel-original-movies-marathon-northern-lights-sharpays-fabulous-adventure/ |title=Why Is The Disney Channel Original Movie Marathon Missing One Major Film?  |work=MTV News |date=June 15, 2016 |access-date=2017-03-16 |quote=The 1997 film ''Northern Lights'', which is widely considered to be the first Disney Channel Original Movie, is not on the list. Some fans, however, peg the DCOM ''Under Wraps'', about a mummy brought back to life, as the first-ever DCOM. Either way, ''Under Wraps'' is certainly more well-known than ''Northern Lights'', which starred Diane Keaton.}}</ref> it was not included in Disney Channel's 100 Original Movies celebration that aired in May\u2013June 2016,<ref name=\"BuzzFeed\">{{cite web |first=Casey|last=Rackham |url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/caseyrackham/omg-the-disney-channel-original-movie-schedule-is-here |title=The Complete Disney Channel Original Movie Schedule Is Here And It\u2019s Amazing |work=[[BuzzFeed]] |date=May 24, 2016 |access-date=2017-03-15}}</ref> and Disney Channel considers 1997's ''[[Under Wraps (film)|Under Wraps]]'' to be the first official Disney Channel Original Movie.<ref>{{cite web |first=Patrick|last=Hipes |url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/disney-channel-original-movie-the-swap-dcom-marathon-1201741163/ |title=Disney Channel Original Movie \u2018The Swap\u2019 Set As Network Plans 100-Pic Celebration |work=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |date=April 20, 2016 |access-date=2016-06-27 |quote=The news comes as Disney Channel today unveiled plans for the 100th DCOM Celebration, a summer programming marathon centered on the airing of the network\u2019s 100th original move since 1997 \u2014 the first movie was ''Under Wraps'', and the 100th will be a reimagining of the 1987 film ''Adventures In Babysitting'' which doesn\u2019t have an airdate yet. }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Marc|last=Snetiker |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/06/22/disney-channel-original-movie-stories |title=Disney Channel Original Movies: 12 little-known stories |work=[[Entertainment Weekly]] |date=June 22, 2016 |access-date=2016-06-26 |quote=Disney Channel considers 1997\u2019s ''Under Wraps'' as its first official DCOM...}}</ref>}}\n|}\n;Notes\n{{Reflist|group=\"Note\"}}\n\n==Disney Channel Original Movies==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Film\n! scope=\"col\" data-sort-type=\"date\" | Premiere date\n! scope=\"col\" data-sort-type=\"number\" | Ratings<br/>(millions)\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | {{Abbr|Ref(s)|References}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"1\" | 1997\n|''[[Under Wraps (film)|Under Wraps]]''\n| October 25, 1997\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{TableTBA|N/A}}\n| <ref name=mtv1>{{cite news|author=Stacey Grant|title=What Is The Best Disney Channel Original Movie Of All Time? Vote Now|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2749351/best-dcom-of-all-time-ranking-dcom/|work=MTV News|publisher=MTV|date=March 7, 2016|access-date=2017-03-15}}</ref> <!-- cite for most of the first 98 -->\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"3\" | 1998\n|''[[You Lucky Dog]]''\n| June 27, 1998\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{TableTBA|N/A}}\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Brink!]]''\n| August 29, 1998\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{TableTBA|N/A}}\n|\n|-\n|''[[Halloweentown (film)|Halloweentown]]''\n| October 17, 1998\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | 3.4\n|<ref name=mtv1/><ref name=\"V-RtHT\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"8\" | 1999\n|''[[Zenon: Girl of the 21st Century (film)|Zenon: Girl of the 21st Century]]''\n| January 23, 1999\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{TableTBA|N/A}}\n|<ref name=mtv1/>\n|-\n|''[[Can of Worms (film)|Can of Worms]]''\n| April 10, 1999\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" 